title: Draymond Green loved MSU beating 'cocky and arrogant' Michigan
text:
Draymond Green loved MSU beating 'cocky and arrogant' Michigan College Spun 12 hrs ago Andrew Holleran © Mike Carter-USA TODAY Sports Former Michigan State Spartans forward Draymond Green was excited about his alma mater's win over Michigan. How does Draymond Green, a Michigan State alumnus and one of the best Quote: s in sports, feel about the Spartans’ miracle win against Michigan?
AdChoices Let’s ask him.
Unsurprisingly, his answer is perfect.
Draymond to KNBR: "Especially if u know how cocky & arrogant people are from Michigan, to beat them like that, that's better than anything."
— Diamond Leung (@diamond83) October 20, 2015
Never change, Draymond.
